      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and remains a solid, dependable choice for your daily commute. While the engine and transmission are mechanically sound and have been serviced regularly, the car shows noticeable signs of its age, including some exterior scratches and interior wear on the upholstery. It\u2019s a reliable workhorse that has plenty of life left for a buyer who prioritizes function over aesthetics.",
