    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This expertly maintained vehicle represents a distinguished acquisition for the discerning motorist. It features a robust powertrain and a well-preserved interior, reflecting a consistent standard of care. Having undergone a comprehensive mechanical assessment, this unit offers a reliable driving experience and exceptional structural integrity. It stands as a premier choice for those seeking a balance of performance and long-term value.",
