    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my reliable ride and it\u2019s been such a treat to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so you can count on it to get you where you need to go comfortably. It runs beautifully and looks great too! I\u2019m looking for a smooth transition to a new owner who will appreciate it as much as I have. Feel free to drop me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
