      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused BMW E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies. This chassis delivers exceptional feedback through its hydraulic rack-and-pinion steering and a factory-spec variable M differential lock. The ZF 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate engagement, while the suspension retains its original composure with firm damping and intact bushings. Essential preventive maintenance, including the VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, has been completed to ensure structural and mechanical longevity. This is a mechanically stout example ready for spirited B-road use.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Clean title. Fully operational. No mechanical issues. Interior well-kept.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle has been a reliable companion and remains in impressive shape. The exterior retains a beautiful luster, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the front fascia\u2014typical of highway driving but hardly noticeable from a few feet away. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the premium upholstery shows only light softening on the driver\u2019s bolster, and all power features, including the dual-zone climate control and infotainment system, function perfectly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with a consistent maintenance record, including a recent oil change and a multi-point inspection. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the transmission shifts seamlessly. It\u2019s a turn-key car that balances performance and comfort, ready for its next chapter with a new owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies consistent care and reliable performance. This unit has undergone a rigorous professional assessment to ensure mechanical integrity and aesthetic standards meet our firm's criteria for quality. Offering a balanced combination of longevity and value, it remains a premier choice for the discerning driver seeking a dependable pre-owned asset. Experience the confidence of a vehicle that performs as well as it presents.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s still got plenty of life left in her? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s been absolute gold for me. She\u2019s in really solid shape, super comfortable for those long weekend drives, and has been very well-loved. It\u2019s the perfect blend of style and dependability without breaking the bank! I'd love to see her go to a great new home, so come take a look and let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a 2011 Porsche Cayman S featuring the refined 987.2 platform. This specimen is powered by a mid-mounted 3.4L flat-six engine equipped with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), eliminating the IMS bearing concerns of predecessors while providing a linear power band and high-revving peak output. The drivetrain is anchored by a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox, offering short-throw precision and optimal gear synchronization. The chassis maintains its factory-spec torsional rigidity, supported by a meticulously maintained MacPherson strut suspension geometry that ensures neutral handling characteristics and minimal body roll under lateral load. The braking system retains excellent pedal feel with ventilated rotors and multi-piston calipers providing consistent heat dissipation. While the exterior shows honest signs of spirited use, the mechanical vitals\u2014including the cooling system's heat exchangers and the dry-sump lubrication\u2014are in robust operational health.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
